display_long_description:
Get ready to test your driving precision and parking skills in Parking Simulator: Car Driving School — the most realistic and challenging car parking game designed for true driving lovers. Whether you’re a beginner or an expert, this simulator will take your parking abilities to the next level!

Drive through detailed parking environments, maneuver around obstacles, and park luxury cars, sedans, and SUVs with perfect accuracy. Each level is carefully crafted to challenge your control, timing, and focus — giving you a real driving school experience right from your phone.

Enjoy smooth controls, realistic physics, and high-quality graphics that make every move feel real. From tight corners to complex multi-level parking lots, Parking Simulator: Car Driving School will test every aspect of your driving skills.

💠 Features:
- Realistic car handling and driving physics
- Smooth steering, acceleration, and braking controls
- Variety of vehicles including SUVs, and luxury cars
- Challenging levels with increasing difficulty
- High-quality 3D graphics and detailed environments
- Realistic sound effects and smooth gameplay performance
- Master the art of car parking and become a pro driver.
